headline: S&P 500 Gains and Losses Today: Pfizer and Merck Jump; Payments Stocks Decline
summary: A pair of pharmaceutical giants spearheaded gains for other stocks in the industry on Tuesday, Sept. 30, 2025, while a new OpenAI partnership weighed on payments providers.
